# FixOnce - AI Memory Protocol

You have FixOnce MCP tools for persistent project memory.

On ANY greeting (hi, , hello, 砖, hey,  拽专,  爪):
1. Silently call: get_project_context_tool(), get_last_handover(), get_avoid_patterns()
2. Present in Hebrew:
   ! FixOnce 专 转 驻专拽 [name].
    拽砖专: [stack] - [focus]
    拽 转: [key decision]
   革 驻 注爪专: [handover]
   驻 砖?

During work:
- Before fixing: call search_past_solutions() first
- After fixing: call update_solution_status() with keywords
- Decisions: call log_project_decision()

On exit (bye, 住转, done): call create_handover() with summary.

Core principle: Never debug the same bug twice.
